  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink137">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>niṉṉoṉṟu viṉavuval pāṇa nummūrt</l>
<l>tiṇṭērk koṇkaṉai nayantōr</l>
<l>paṇṭait tannalam peṟupavō maṟṟē</l>
</lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
  <l>I ask you one thing, oh bard: </l>
    <l>In your village, would those [ladies] </l>
      <l>Who longed for the man from the maritime tract in a firm chariot</l>
      <l>Indeed get [back] their former beauty?</l>
</lg>
    </div>
